1254
01:34:24,451 --> 01:34:28,872
And that was going on
for the live-action stuff as well.

1255
01:34:29,122 --> 01:34:32,167
It requires that you be very flexible.

1256
01:34:32,376 --> 01:34:37,631
You have to be willing to abandon
a scene that you like that you've...

1257
01:34:37,798 --> 01:34:42,427
...spent months developing since
