1258
01:34:42,678 --> 01:34:47,224
That's the hardest thing in doing
visual effects and filmmaking...

1259
01:34:47,474 --> 01:34:50,936
...is giving away your "babies,"
so to speak...

1260
01:34:51,144 --> 01:34:54,940
...in pursuit of a more
effective storytelling.

1261
01:34:55,190 --> 01:34:58,652
You also have to be willing to meet...

1262
01:34:58,861 --> 01:35:03,490
...an impossible challenge at the last
moment. When we did this film...

1263
01:35:03,740 --> 01:35:07,619
...it wasn't unusual
in the last two or three weeks...

1264
01:35:07,870 --> 01:35:13,250
...for the director and editor to
come up with a shot that required...

1265
01:35:13,417 --> 01:35:15,377
...some heroic performance.

1266
01:35:15,586 --> 01:35:20,507
We talked about one of the shots
