1270
01:35:34,605 --> 01:35:40,986
...and willing to pursue the end
goal of the story, first and foremost.

1271
01:35:41,194 --> 01:35:46,783
Seems like on every film,
you always promise something...

1272
01:35:46,992 --> 01:35:50,621
...that you have no idea
whether or not you can do.

1273
01:35:50,787 --> 01:35:52,039
You have to.

1274
01:35:52,205 --> 01:35:56,835
And that's generally how new ways
of doing things are created.

1275
01:35:57,044 --> 01:36:00,589
What's interesting
