effects or stunts.

1278
01:36:08,597 --> 01:36:12,059
Other filmmakers I've
worked with have defaulted...

1279
01:36:12,267 --> 01:36:14,853
...to a digital solution immediately.

1280
01:36:15,020 --> 01:36:20,692
He'd explore more traditional methods
extensively before allocating...

1281
01:36:20,859 --> 01:36:26,406
...that visual effects resource
to a single shot or a sequence.

1282
01:36:26,573 --> 01:36:32,454
And I think that that shows up
in his understanding of this story.

1283
01:36:32,663 --> 01:36:37,084
He knows where he wants
to put the money, the resource...

