1326
01:39:47,149 --> 01:39:50,026
"Physically, this couldn't happen."

1327
01:39:50,277 --> 01:39:55,407
So the sequences that you see here,
swing from one end of the pole...

1328
01:39:55,615 --> 01:39:59,619
